529
00:36:05,246 --> 00:36:06,497
- REALLY?
- MM-HMM.

530
00:36:06,497 --> 00:36:08,124
FUCK YOU.

531
00:36:08,124 --> 00:36:10,126
NO, FUCK YOU.
